{"tid":944804,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你啦","createTime":"2018-12-17T11:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T13:25:03.000Z","uid":225828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"44bdd78911bdb5ea3b5dfd54de9979eb43960450","tid":944804,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T11:54:18.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母啦林鄭,山竹都唔撚畀人放假,將打工仔當狗咁撚,講埋唒啲咩希望僱主會體諒依啲攞景贈興嘢,仲話自己係上帝叫你參選,咁撚冇人性我就話你係魔鬼代言人幫魔鬼暫時管理住香港喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又將啲私人恩怨擺落社會政策到,死唔跟薯片嗰套搞到派嗰四千都派到柒吓柒咁,你唔好逼人叫你做柒婆啦好嘛,你唔要面你屋企人都要面㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講到自己咁打得,連照顧自己日常生活買廁紙用八達通都唔識,弱智人士都醒個你啦,高分低能！自己咁高學歴要聽個小學畢業嘅點嚟點去,讀屎片㗎你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人哋國家元首互相角力,好心你就縮返入你太婆個閪喥啦,莊閒都唔識分,把閪口剩係識噴埋啲咩「美國行單邊主義」、「美國唔好干涉香港內政嘅」嘅狗屎,你主子有冇批准你奶佢鞋底呀Carriage Lam 林馬車？都仲未提你老母臭/湊 大你,你竟然走去做宦官？以為同人哋侵侵咁高咁大？喂餵,企開啲啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時我真係好鄧葉劉唔抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解當年畀麒麟撞嘅係佢,唔係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聖誕節就到喇,如果聖誕老人畀我一份聖誕禮物,我希望佢可以用鹿車車鳩你,然後叫埋啲咩嘢聖誕小精靈、寵物小精靈、數碼暴龍同埋妖怪手錶一齊代天道揼柒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後變走唒你新年啲利是錢做樹葉同埋溪錢,等你可以過一個乜鳩都冇嘅新年：Happy New Year <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe16273ac52418785a232447595ced7d20d4d210","tid":944804,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T06:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />高汁"},{"pid":"b618900413845c135841328247654312d3c721ef","tid":944804,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe16273ac52418785a232447595ced7d20d4d210","tid":944804,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T06:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />高汁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T13:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}